&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a change why not come and join our &lt;strong&gt; friendly &lt;/strong&gt;team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint motivated and enthusiastic Maternity Nurses who can provide high quality care to our women and families and provide immediate individualised nursing care to women who have undergone operative procedures. To work alongside the maternity team ensuring The Princess Alexandra Hospital NHS Trust is the preferred place of birth as well as the preferred place of employment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you believe you have the energy, drive, talent and skillset come and join our team, for an informal discussion or to arrange to visit the hospital contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sue Callaghan - Inpatient Maternity Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01279 827103&lt;/p&gt;
